cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.CR, cs.SD 

The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques for detecting digital deception and disinformation spread across social platforms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with NLP. The paper also discusses multimodal deception detection from images and text, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses the limitations of image-only and text-only models, which falls under the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also discusses the spread of disinformation across social platforms, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
